			"subclassSource": "Smooth Criminal",
			"level": 3,
			"entries": [
				"一些流氓通过魔法增强他们精湛的潜行和敏捷技能，学习了吟游诗人的表演秘密。这些流氓包括(rogues)窃贼、恶作剧者、捣蛋鬼，以及大量的冒险家。",
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Spellcasting|Rogue||Smooth|Smooth Criminal|3"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
